-- David Beckham Rejected Transfer Request From Sao Paulo FC, Goal.com Says
-- B y   L a u r a   P r i c e
-- 2010-12-22T17:02:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-22/david-beckham-rejected-transfer-request-from-sao-paulo-fc-goal-com-says.html
David Beckham rejected a request to
transfer to Sao Paulo FC, Goal.com reported, citing an interview
by Milton Cruz, an assistant coach for the Brazilian team, on
the Jovem Pan radio station.  Cruz approached the Los Angeles Galaxy soccer star during a
chance meeting in the U.S., Goal said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
